Before you start the Zend Server (standalone) you will have to obtain a trial license or locate you current Zend Server license.

For trial license request open the following link:http://www.zend.com/products/server/license

Please refer to ZendServerPHPApplicationServerStandalone.pdf for blueprint information.

After the successful deployment Zend Server UI will be available at ports 10081 and 10082.
You can make additional customization of your PHP settings though the UI.

Zend Server documentation can be found at the following link:
http://files.zend.com/help/Zend-Server/zend-server.htm 

Zend API reference information can be found at the following link:
http://files.zend.com/help/Zend-Server/zend-server.htm#web_api_reference_guide.htm

